room_title: Escape room "Area 51" by EXcape Columbus in Columbus
room_description: Half of your team is trapped in the mother ship, the other half is trying to rescue them but there are two locked doors of a third room between you. Your team will have to find ways to communicate from separate rooms, transport items through a tunnel and reunite. Once together, continue to work together to excape the center room in 60 minutes or left.
